Preconditions:
- The input string "s" should not be null.
- The input array "indices" should not be null.
- The length of the input string "s" should be equal to the length of the input array "indices".

Postconditions:
- The returned string should be a shuffled version of the input string "s".
- The characters in the returned string should be arranged according to the indices provided in the input array "indices".